Here's what each field means:

- `name` — the full name shown during installation
- `short_name` — the label shown under the icon on the home screen (keep it under 12 characters)
- `display: "standalone"` — this is the key setting that removes the browser bar and makes it look like a native app
- `background_color` — the color shown on the splash screen while the app loads
- `theme_color` — the color of the status bar at the top of the phone
- `orientation: "portrait"` — locks the app to portrait mode (remove this line if you want it to rotate)

